{"tid":89487,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[剃鬚研究區]  剃鬚刀 VS 剃鬚刨，同埋買邊隻型號好？","createTime":"2017-01-21T11:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T08:22:52.000Z","uid":54684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cb21cb23d7608ac9f2b04be582b33d32fbb437b","tid":89487,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:15:16.000Z","msg":"Case Study︰<br />\n小弟鬚多 + 密<br />\n剃盡都會見到少少黑點(鬚根)，雖然摸上手塊面已經係100%滑，摸唔到鬚根<br />\n朝早剃完<br />\n放工已經生返少少黑色鬚根出來<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSolution︰<br />\n我以前用開Braun個隻Series 5<br />\n有清潔座<br />\n<img src=\"http://bestelectricshave.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Braun-series-5-590cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbestelectricshave.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F02%2FBraun-series-5-590cc.jpg&h=757942e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前個排試用Gilette 個D剃刀<br />\n類似呢種<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.voyager.pgsitecore.com/en-us/-/media/Gillette/Images/Products/Razors%20and%20Blades/gillette-fusion-power-razor-techFEB2015.jpg?la=en-US&amp;v=1-201502261732\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.voyager.pgsitecore.com%2Fen-us%2F-%2Fmedia%2FGillette%2FImages%2FProducts%2FRazors%2520and%2520Blades%2Fgillette-fusion-power-razor-techFEB2015.jpg%3Fla%3Den-US%26v%3D1-201502261732&h=6284e823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n覺得更貼面<br />\n<br />\n但我係順剃完 再 逆剃<br />\n去清下頷骨位置 (下巴 既  左同右兩邊) 個D鬚根<br />\n要逆剃幾次<br />\n<br />\n結果係可以90%全面鬚根摸唔到<br />\n下巴 既  左同右兩邊 既 鬚根   就清剩少少<br />\n算係very good<br />\n好過 剃鬚刨<br />\n更貼面<br />\n全塊面多數地方摸上手   都好滑手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係  下巴 既  左同右兩邊  <br />\n就好易有D紅<br />\n因為係咁刮   刺激到佢地<br />\n聽講如果長期係咁  會有手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQuestion︰<br />\n我想貼面  徹底  見人唔失禮得來<br />\n係唔會太傷皮膚<br />\n我又唔太要求短時間剃鬚   剃鬚需時長短 not a big deal<br />\n1. 我應該用剃鬚刀 / 剃鬚刨？<br />\n2. 推介咩型號 for 我去買？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9683d938f0390664e382d6af9b2614ce9b78286c","tid":89487,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"用開剃刀,1鎊4支4刀片"},{"pid":"27601c77cd6d615c9a33d3882fee00bedb105cc1","tid":89487,"uid":3249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:19:27.000Z","msg":"之前睇過呢度一個post之後走咗去買safety razor，依家感覺良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0b30fd6e6b35737ee26bbce3e93e1b8c08d380","tid":89487,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"279931fe6e6375cf9951d044d3c76d775ef73746","tid":89487,"uid":3173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:51:21.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"21240d863bc750e5d36a15e4fd249822dea5b2c6","tid":89487,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"Safety razor邊到有得買？"},{"pid":"d5bfb60af9ada2efd080a488f5815196d9d1f59c","tid":89487,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"刀配合膏一定好d"},{"pid":"ed0bb38329de89516e1c56ee59a3b923c608df63","tid":89487,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"以前用電，個頸位完全剃唔到<br />\n<br />\n而家用緊吉列最新嗰隻剃刀，好貼，剃得乾淨"},{"pid":"b96f3250ec355d25e85c024e931111f3a9a11f37","tid":89487,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:57:45.000Z","msg":"d鬼佬話 2 blade 以上係 unnecessary<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人認為 2 blade 就應付到基本需要, 3 blade 都得.<br />\n5 blade 完全係 gillette 玩出黎嘅gimmick"},{"pid":"94c73fc975088c22de2542087df9221623db333e","tid":89487,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"straight razor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72410906a6bbce2637f4fd708a5ae96394fb42df","tid":89487,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d鬼佬話 2 blade 以上係 unnecessary<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人認為 2 blade 就應付到基本需要, 3 blade 都得.<br />\n5 blade 完全係 gillette 玩出黎嘅gimmick</blockquote><br />\n但你用過就知道真係有分別，如果3 blade個效果係90分，5 blade就係95分。話就話分別唔太明顯，但價錢亦都無話貴好多，所以都算值得用。"},{"pid":"a772e19fea13846055fc6c26b2aa588cd377bc83","tid":89487,"uid":24155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:50:03.000Z","msg":"雖然用剃刀係乾淨啲<br />\n但用好易敏感 時不時會剃損<br />\n所以都係用返電鬚刨<br />\n<br />\n用緊9095cc"},{"pid":"5cdcf32482d9096951a36a3052e79381feb786a9","tid":89487,"uid":14009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:55:06.000Z","msg":"我都係用手動<br />\n公司先用電"},{"pid":"ed74c2f4d2d0efd384ec205ca7391f35b9525d18","tid":89487,"uid":14009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"沖完涼<br />\nd鬚軟曬先剃<br />\n就唔傷㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n膏都唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb87b70b48b8f61e8a13b3afd38f1d578a8375d","tid":89487,"uid":2741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/143912_4f4c12d987edcb61ee1830bd6d6cc783.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F20